We hope you love shopping with Venia. Here

column1: are our delivery and returns policies to help make sure we meet your
Shipping and
Shipping and Delivery is the charge for internet order
processing, item selection, packaging, transport and handling.
We don’t guarantee delivery times, but we do our best to provide
Deliveries occur only on weekdays. Shipping and Delivery charges
are subject to change and are determined when you order.
Estimated delivery time assumes orders are placed before 12:00
noon (PST). Orders you place with Venia late on Friday or on
Saturday will not be processed until Monday. Charges may be
added to orders with Priority, Overnight and International
shipping if we try unsuccessfully to deliver your order more
Delivery addresses in Alaska, Hawaii, Puerto Rico, and Guam
should add an additional $5.00 charge for standard Shipping

column2: Delivery. Orders arrive in 7 to 9 business days when

column3: >**after processing if ordered by 12:00 noon PST

column1: Returns and

Replacements

We want you to be completely happy with your

column2: order. If for any reason you are not satisfied, we will

column1: gladly accept your timely return of unworn, unwashed, or defective
merchandise. Used merchandise cannot be returned unless defective.
Returned merchandise should include the vendor packaging and tags
and be in the same condition as when it was received. A pickup
and/or restock fee may apply. Merchandise must be returned within 30
days of receipt of merchandise.

Returning Merchandise by Mail

On the back of the packing slip

column1: enclosed with your Venia order, please note the reason(s)
for return and whether you wish to exchange the item(s) or
receive a credit/refund (depending on the original form of
Enclose the return section of the packing slip with your
item(s). Please use one of the return labels provided on
the front of your packing slip to ensure proper return
address and credit information. Restricted items must be
Please allow 10 to 14 days for Venia to process your

return.

Returning Gifts

When returning a gift, a Venia Gift
Card will be issued to the gift recipient for the amount of
the returned merchandise. The card can be used for purchases
from any Venia store, and online.
In compliance with Federal law, for gifts valued at more
than $2,000.00, the recipient will receive a check

>We are committed to providing responsibly manufactured apparel and accessories that excite and inspire our customers.

About Us

Venia, founded in 2009, is a globally recognized apparel manufacturer and retailer, with more than 230 locations in the US and Canada, and selling to 96 countries worldwide through our website.

column1:
We differentiate ourselves through a combination of unique designs and styles merged with unequaled standards of quality and authenticity by partnering with the best, ethical factories around the world and sourcing the finest materials.

Our Mission
column2: To provide high-quality products that excite and inspire a diverse global community. &nbsp
